{"tid":951567,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NIKE 真實版《回到未來 2》自動綁帶球鞋 2019 年上市　售價為 350 美元","createTime":"2018-12-22T12:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T08:26:32.000Z","uid":212399,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e68565f5ae8730ef797823800105692b57602a47","tid":951567,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/media/post/image/3/6/36.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fmedia%2Fpost%2Fimage%2F3%2F6%2F36.png&h=de8c5583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲NIKE 真實版《回到未來 2》自動綁帶球鞋 2019 年上市。（圖／翻攝自NIKE）<br />\n吳佳臻／綜合報導<br />\n1989 年電影《回到未來 2》中，主角腳上那雙自動繫鞋帶球鞋 Air Mag，不再遙不可及！NIKE 近日宣布 HyperAdapt 2.0 智慧球鞋，將於 2019 年春季上市，售價為 350 美元（約新台幣 1 萬 1 千元）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xQLb_uwWzj8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxQLb_uwWzj8&d=RBEWNUJz0QdmPTNU9652XMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=2cf39338\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xQLb_uwWzj8</a><br />\n▲NIKE 曾打造出真實版《回到未來 2》Nike Air Mag。<br />\n根據《engadget》報導，NIKE 在季度結算報告中宣佈，有計劃於 2019 年推出具有自動鞋帶調整功能的智慧球鞋。追溯至 2015 年，NIKE 曾打造出真實版《回到未來 2》Nike Air Mag，並將這雙自動綁帶球鞋贈送給飾演主角的 Michael J. Fox。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JWnw4hnzkJ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJWnw4hnzkJ8&d=RBEWNUJz0QdmPTNU9652XMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=496b1c4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JWnw4hnzkJ8</a><br />\n▲2016 年發表同具自動綁帶功能的鞋子「HyperAdapt 1.0」。<br />\n爾後，2016 年發表同具自動綁帶功能的鞋子「HyperAdapt 1.0」，該鞋款設計與電影中的 Nike Air Mag 大為不同，是一雙較為實用的跑步鞋。然而，其要價 720 美元（約新台幣 2 萬 2 千元），且採限量生產，為一般人無法入手的夢幻逸品。<br />\n這回發表的新鞋款，可稱之為「HyperAdapt 2.0」，350 美元（約新台幣 1 萬 1 千元）的價格，使得它不再遙不可及。而採籃球鞋設計的它，可能會比 HyperAdapt 1.0 更接近 Nike Air Mag 的設計。據悉，於自動鞋帶調整功能方面，可能採與前一代不同類型的智慧技術。<br />\nNIKE 執行長 Mark Parker 表示，我們創造了能實現完美貼合感的智慧鞋，這是將數位化轉型與產品連接起來的重要一步。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.limitlessiq.com/news/post/view/id/8209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.limitlessiq.com%2Fnews%2Fpost%2Fview%2Fid%2F8209%2F&d=RBEWNUJz0QdmPTNU9652XMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=ee779351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.limitlessiq.com/news/post/view/id/8209/</a>"},{"pid":"cb6f5df4d475f075cf255b9e34512c1a1afff489","tid":951567,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9fefd6e6e02d561a630e9d722f8fa39d322caf0","tid":951567,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"818304a0e81feb05d6e5c206c95120ce41a8f0a1","tid":951567,"uid":53122,"like":8,"dislike":14,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:32:03.000Z","msg":"睇番d幾十年科技無點進步過<br />\n<br />\n飛天車<br />\n飛行滑板<br />\n都未實用化"},{"pid":"3c650116d598340d292e178a25bd0d7939418fa3","tid":951567,"uid":19557,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"3千銀買對鞋 留返比潮童玩"},{"pid":"ca847ecf713868e7316373f0bad5916ab9e9250d","tid":951567,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:41:42.000Z","msg":"好撚柒"},{"pid":"3cbefc8b096d561c2109d2acea0c468ec759a5c0","tid":951567,"uid":52595,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:43:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f6bd05a091703f55255c66e9fa10a713b05a3d4","tid":951567,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:43:35.000Z","msg":"350美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8b8dac4beed328d459673018bb096c5f367313","tid":951567,"uid":214036,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:48:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f47fe3ac7e7f9d9b23236bf994cd35953aa4b95","tid":951567,"uid":24345,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"818304a0e81feb05d6e5c206c95120ce41a8f0a1","tid":951567,"uid":53122,"like":8,"dislike":14